Mission.Author: KingRaptor
Mission.Description: Ada finds a Machine world that is not as abandoned as it seems to be.
Mission.Name: Sunrise Episode 4M - Ambush at Rossum

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Ada") --Spring.SetUnitPosition()
local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Dereg") for unitID in pairs(units) do GG.CAI.RemoveUnit(unitID) end

GG.CAI.SuspendAI(1, true) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryamph.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factorycloak.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryveh.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factorytank.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryhover.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryjump.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryspider.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factorygunship.id, 0) GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, UnitDefNames.factoryplane.id, 0)

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: The Free Machines have ambushed you. Turn things around and destroy their commander and factories.
TriggerLogic.Title: Defeat Ambush

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Let me tell you one of our favorite jokes, Ada Caedmon. "To serve man."
What?
It's a cookbook.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Skirmishers. I'm dropping you some Pyros now.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message: The Pyro is a fast jumper unit focused on raiding. Its short-ranged flamethrower is particularly effective against large, wide units (like factories) and swarmers, and can ignite them for damage over time. It has high health (for a raider) and thus resists many riot weapons quite well, but is vulnerable to things normally ineffective against lighter units. When killed, Pyros explode in a burst of flame.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Outlaws incoming. Moderators should give them a taste of their own medicine.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message: The Moderator skirmisher bot fires a medium-ranged disruptor beam that significantly slows and damages enemy units. It has a 10 second reload time, low HP and can't jump out of a fight, so make your shots count.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Thug push. Time to Jack this up a notch.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message: Slow, ugly, and extremely terrifying. The Jack is a jumping assault unit with a melee weapon that can turn most things to scrap in short order, and penetrates shields. It is deadly against anything that can't run away.
We need to crush the Free Machines and stop them from impeding our progress any further. Take out their leader and any factories they've set up.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: A Firewalker may help with fire support.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message:
The Firewalker is an expensive artillery walker whose shots leave firestorms on the ground, denying access to light units. It can burn clumps of light units and defences (including those with personal shields), but is completely ineffective against area shields.
Like all artillery units, it is vulnerable in close combat.
Your blood will flow freely today, oppressor. We shall not yield to your kind.
I have no time for you, machine. Get out of the way!
Over my dead body.

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Ada") local _,_,_,x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID, true) Spring.SpawnCEG("gate", x, y, z) Spring.SpawnCEG("teleport_out", x, y, z) Spring.PlaySoundFile("sounds/misc/teleport.wav", 2.0, x, y, z, nil, nil, nil, "sfx") Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID, false, true)

TriggerLogic.Message: Emergency teleport successful.

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("FreeMachine") local _,_,_,x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID, true) Spring.SpawnCEG("gate", x, y, z) Spring.SpawnCEG("teleport_out", x, y, z) Spring.PlaySoundFile("sounds/misc/teleport.wav", 2.0, x, y, z, nil, nil, nil, "sfx") Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID, false, true)

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Accursed despot... Do not think this is over!

TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Ada") if unitID then GG.SetUnitInvulnerable(unitID, true) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.STOP, {}, 0) end
Spring.KillTeam(1)

TriggerLogic.Message: One challenge dealt with.
Indeed... but I fear they will only become harder from here on out.
Thus ever to tyrants.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Here we are.
Mm, surprisingly well-maintained. Alright, let's get this place up and running.
Welcome to our web, little insect.
